'desc': [u'

Mozo All in One Feeding Bottle Set (Pink)

The 16 piece infant starter kit included everything that you need to feed and nurture your baby. It includes milk bottles in various sizes
column18:
feeding spoon and fork and few essential grooming products. The feeding bottles have automatic vents to adjust the milk volume according to babys requirement and prevent chocking. \n ']
